STATE
v.
Ronald P. CAMERON 164P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 19, 2019 Ronald P. Cameron, for Cameron, Ronald P. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st of May 2019 by Defendant to Dismiss Prosecution:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of June 2019."
